information:
Disposable Time X ANTI
ZXRX, 12.10.24, 23h

@disposable.time and @____________anti______________ joined forces and are going all out. Two floors, a Soli cocktail bar and awesome music in one of Leipzigs mythological places.

L.F.T. - live
@love.fist.tears from Hamburg/Berlin live in Leipzig for the first time. An analog hellbrew and acidbath of emotions made of wavy synths, distorted basslines and broken kick drums.

Bound by Endogamy - live
@bound_by_endogamy from Geneva delivers furious synthwave with industrial influences, snotty vocals and live drums. A fever dream in which Kleenex wander through the apocalypse and put DAF in a chokehold.

Leroy se Meurt - live
@leroysemeurt from Paris deliver electro punk enriched with cold wave, EBM and a good portion of frustration, which is roared out to nasty synthlines.

En Direct - live
Between Leipzig and Rotterdam, electro and wave-melancholy, broken open-cast mines and rattling synths. @_en_direct will be performing live for the first time. They will be presenting their new album. It's very good.

PRZ - live
Electro of the highest order from Tel Aviv/Berlin. Not averse to rave without getting cheesy, sometimes tricky, then straight forward again. @__p.r.z__ is always a special treat live.

